---
title: Asian-Spiced Chicken & Honey-Soy Veggies with Jasmine Rice & Sesame Mayo
description: Watch out because our lovely chicken is going to turn some heads tonight! This deliciously tender protein is the star of the show, sitting on a bed of fluffy rice and honey-soy veg with a sesame mayo drizzle. Go on, dig in!

